OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry, some late brightness in
OL,7,Fthe south. Then the rest of the night
OL,8,Fwill remain dry and becoming rather
OL,9,Fcloudy. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FAll parts will have a dry
OL,12,Fday. Rather cloudy in the morning but
OL,13,Fa few brighter spells in the afternoon.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry and
OL,16,Fwarm with bright spells on Friday.
OL,17,FCloudy with outbreaks of rain on
OL,18,FSaturday then mainly dry on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
